        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.izync.com/">Zync</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Some friends&#8217; startup.  It&#8217;s going to evolve into smart &#8220;social search&#8221;.  In the meantime, Bostonfolks:  Try training their brain (It&#8217;s fun!) and seeing how well it knows you.</p>

