<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jul/14/">&#x27a0;</a> July 14, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="twttr" >

        
        <a name="002697"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://twttr.com/">twttr</a></h4>

        

        <p>New mobile friend-tracking social-network system from some Odeo folks.  It reminds me of the way my friends and I used to use our AIM Away and Profile messages to pass on information and injokes.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
