<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/mar/13/">&#x27a0;</a> March 13, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="skobee" >

        
        <a name="002316"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.skobee.com/">Skobee</a></h4>

        

        <p>I missed their session at ETech (Thursday morning was sleepytime for Rod), but this app looks cool.  It&#8217;s like a fuzzy evite &#8212; Contact your friends to say &#8220;Let&#8217;s do something next week&#8221;, then let the software manage when people are available and what they want to do.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
