<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/oct/28/">&#x27a0;</a> October 28, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="ljnet_livejournal_social_netwo" >

        
        <a name="002084"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://patrickbarry.com/projects/ljnet/">LJNet - LiveJournal Social Network Visualization</a></h4>

        

        <p>This is rather fun &#8212; It maps out your friends-of-friends-of-friends network from LiveJournal.  It takes a long time to run, but the output is nifty.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
